Name: Chiptune DJ
About the game: Be a DJ in this chiptune based Rhythm game. Play with mouse and keyboard and improve your coordination skills while listening retro chiptune music with beatifull pixel art backgrounds that move on beats. - More than 12 chiptune songs to play - Various difficulties for each skill level - Pixel art backgrounds for each song - Track your progress with highscores - Try to get Perfect performance by not missing any notes - Mouse+keyboard gameplay - Easy mode avaible if you find it too difficult - Might continue adding more songs in the future
